description.standard:
Celebrating our Birthday --> LIMITED TIME Sale! (normally $9.99, NOW only $2.99) ---> DOWNLOAD NOW<---

InstaLogo transforms your iPhone, iPad and iPod into portable logo creators. It allows you to create unique logos, flyers, posters, invitation cards or any design, anywhere. In under 3 minutes!

Created logos can be emailed and printed, uploaded to Dropbox, Evernote and Box, or simply saved on the iPhone/iPad/iPod.
 
The best logo design application on the market. Check out the screenshots and see for yourself. You will not be disappointed!

InstaLogo gives you an easy way to make logos for your business, product, organization, presentation & more.

------
What Customers Are Saying:

„This is simply amazing. Wasn't expecting it to be this good when I downloaded. Can't stop creating.“ - by Benjtee

„Definitely worth adding to your app collection. Wished I had found this before I paid a lot of cash to designers....“ - by christofim

„It is the best logo design app I've seen in a while 5 STARS!!“ - by Dragoman7

„This is an awesome app. It's easy. It's fun. It's incredibly useful. Well done!“ - by IrocOn1
------


Create beautiful logos
- Choose from our huge library of logos
- Import photos from photo library
- Tons of fonts to select from or you can even import your favorite fonts
- Copy and paste anything from and to the app
- Pinch, drag and spin your logo elements to change sizes

Adjust & modify each part of your logo
- Full featured gradient color editor on logos, texts and on the background
- Professional shadow editor on logos, texts, photos and drawings
- Undo-redo every step you make: 1000 levels of undo and redo are available
- Use grid lines that help in the alignment of each part of the logo to graphics
- Apply degree indicators for professional results 

Release your creativity
- Draw with your finger: use it to unleash your full potential
- Eraser: rub out any part of a logo, or the whole logo easily
- Lasso tool : correct any mistake, any time. The lasso tool lets you move things around

Saving
- Save your logos as: PNG/JPEG/PDF
- Gives the option of saving and sharing as Transparent PNGs

Sharing and uploading your logos
- Access to various types of cloud services to upload and store your logos: Dropbox, Evernote, Box
- Share your logos by email or facebook
- Printing: print any of your logos with AirPrint enabled printers

With our Professional Color Picker
- Choose any color you can dream of right away with the natural color picker 
- Hue, saturation and brightness sliders accompany a large color circle with an additional RGB color selector
- Your latest colors are saved to a palette automatically while you create your logos 
- You can also save your favorite colors to a palette with drag and drop

iPhone, iPad, iPod
- Supports iPhone, iPad and iPod
- Tested & certified on all product models
- Built using Apple recommended methods

Other Key Features
- Full iOS 8 Support
- 50,000+ possible logo combinations
- Our logos were designed by professional graphic designers 
- All royalty free
- Full Offline: create logos offline, never fear data usage
- We release constant FREE updates with NEW functions

---------------------------------- 
NOTE: iOS 6 Users: You must enable InstaLogo to save logos to your photos. 
Go to SETTINGS / PRIVACY / PHOTOS and click YES for InstaLogo. Enjoy! 
---------------------------------- 

Localized in 34 languages! Use this app in your native language! 
Supported languages: English, Spanish, Catalan, Russian, French, German, Italian, Portuguese, Japanese, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese, Korean, Arabic, Hindi, Thai, Vietnamese, Hebrew, Malay, Afrikaans, Indonesian, Turkish, Swedish, Finnish, Norwegian, Dutch, Danish, Greek, Hungarian, Polish, Slovak, Romanian, Croatian, Ukrainian, Czech

GET 24/7 SUPPORT
Dear customers, we are here for you! Questions? Comments? Support? Just contact us at support@instalogocreator.com


Download InstaLogo Logo Creator NOW, while it’s 70% OFF!
